> ##Code exhibit 3.1  函數 c() 
> x=c(0.5, 1, 2.3, 6.1, 5.5) 
> x 
[1] 0.5 1.0 2.3 6.1 5.5
> y=c(x, 0.25, x) 
> y 
 [1] 0.50 1.00 2.30 6.10 5.50 0.25 0.50 1.00 2.30 6.10 5.50
> z=c(sin(x)/cos(x), log(x)) 
> z 
 [1]  0.5463025  1.5574077 -1.1192136 -0.1852622 -0.9955841 -0.6931472  0.0000000  0.8329091  1.8082888  1.7047481
> w=c("Brazil", "Russia", "India", "China") 
> w 
[1] "Brazil" "Russia" "India"  "China" 
